long_desc.thetext:
Using a model and a controller, it is possible to control the values of a form.
I would like to be able to control the placeholder values with the same model.

It could be look like this:
var form = new qx.ui.form.Form();
var field = new qx.ui.form.TextField();
form.add(field,"username");

var controller = new qx.data.controller.Form(null,form);

controller.createModel();
var model = controller.getModel();

model.setUsernamePlaceHolder("test");
